    Discover the Essence of Wellness

    AAROHA AYURVEDA

    Our Story

    Aaroha Ayurveda was born out of a passion for holistic well-being and a deep appreciation for the natural treasures our planet provides. Our journey began with a simple belief – that true wellness starts with pure, untainted ingredients sourced directly from the heart of nature.

    Our Philosophy

    At Aaroha, we believe in the harmony of mind, body, and spirit. Our Ayurvedic products are crafted with care, reflecting the balance and wisdom of ancient traditions while embracing the needs of the modern world. We strive to provide you with more than just products; we offer a holistic approach to well-being.

    The Aaroha Difference

    What sets us apart is our commitment to authenticity. We go beyond the ordinary, sourcing our ingredients from indigenous communities practicing sustainable harvesting methods. This not only ensures the purity of our products but also supports the livelihoods of those who have been the stewards of these traditions for generations.

    Ethical Sourcing

    We take pride in our ethical sourcing practices. By working directly with forest communities, we contribute to the preservation of natural ecosystems and the empowerment of those who play a vital role in maintaining the delicate balance of our planet.

    Meet the Team

    At Aaroha Ayurveda, our team is a diverse blend of passionate individuals united by a shared commitment to your well-being. Get to know the faces behind the brand, each contributing their unique expertise to bring you the best in Ayurvedic wellness.

    Managing Partner

    REKHA RAVEENDRAN

    As a dynamic leader, Rekha enriches Aaroha Ayurveda with her extensive experience. A qualified Ayurvedic doctor hailing from Thrissur Irinjalakuda, her roots are embedded in the ancient secrets of Ayurveda. Her professional journey is marked by an unwavering passion for Ayurveda, a commitment to sustainability, and an adherence to ethical business practices.

    Founder

    AMAL DAS

    Aaroha Ayurveda is driven by the visionary leadership of Sivadasan Amal Das, a native of Pathanamthitta and our founder at the core. His unwavering commitment to holistic wellness shapes the foundation of our endeavors. Sivadasan Amal Das infuses our Ayurvedic journey with a distinctive combination of tradition, innovation, and unwavering passion.
